


















About EcoBuddy

EcoBuddy is an educational iOS application developed using SwiftUI for the Swift Student Challenge (SSC).

The app helps users:
                   Learn proper waste disposal methods
                   Understand environmental impact
                   Discover creative reuse ideas
                   Practice eco-friendly habits through interactive games

The goal is to make environmental education simple, engaging, and accessible.


🎯 Problem Statement

Many people do not know:
                Which bin to use for different waste
                The environmental impact of daily items
                How long waste takes to decompose
                How to reuse items creatively
EcoBuddy solves this problem by combining education + interaction + gamification.


🚀 Features

📘 1. Browse Eco Items

50+ everyday items
Category filtering
Smart search functionality

🌍 2. EcoLens

Environmental impact overview
Decomposition time
Carbon footprint insights

♻️ 3. SecondLife

Creative reuse ideas
Difficulty levels (Easy, Medium, Advanced)

🗑 4. TrashRight

Correct bin guidance
Step-by-step disposal instructions
Recycling tips

🎮 5. Play & Learn

Waste Collection Game
Interactive sorting activity
Learning through gamification

🛠 Tech Stack
      
Swift
