📦 App Specifications

✅ Lightweight (Under 25MB)
✅ Fully Offline
✅ No third-party libraries
✅ Optimized for Swift Playgrounds

🧠 Architecture

EcoBuddy follows MVVM Architecture:

Model → EcoItem, DisposalType, ReuseIdea

ViewModel → Handles logic and filtering

View → SwiftUI UI Components

This keeps the project clean, scalable, and maintainable.

