💡 Inspiration

EcoBuddy was inspired by the need to create a simple yet powerful tool that encourages sustainable habits in daily life.

📌 Conclusion

EcoBuddy promotes environmental responsibility by making learning: Simple ,Interactive ,Practical,Fun.
   “Small actions today create a greener tomorrow.”
